column8:
The fallacy present in these posts is Appeal to Authority. The posters are referring to #CZ as the authority figure claiming that the bullrun will start from China and #OGGYINU is the right choice to invest in. This is a fallacy because the mere mention of #CZ as an authority figure does not make the argument valid.

Example post:
@AltCryptoGems As per #CZ bullrun will start from china and #OggyInu is focusing there do you got the connection? @OggyInuBrand üëä
